<a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#marincricketclub" class="nav-link">
  <%= image_tag('mcc_website.png', alt: 'Marin Cricket Club', class: 'img-fluid') %>
  <p class="font-weight-bold">
    Marin Cricket Club
  </p>
</a>

<div class="modal fade" id="marincricketclub" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="marincricketclubTitle" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title text-center" id="marincricketclubTitle">Marin Cricket Club</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <%= image_tag('mcc_website.png', alt: 'Marin Cricket Club', id: 'myImg', class: 'img-fluid') %>
        <p class="text-justify">
          For Marin Cricket Club the goal was to allow players to sign up for games, pay for
          memberships and games electornically and to continue to promote the club to public.
          There is a full blown user system, game results, stat tracking and more!
          This is a project that will continue to be updated and evlove over the next few years.
        <p class="text-justify">
          Built with Rails, Bootstrap 4, PostgresQL, Heroku.
        </p>
        <p class="text-justify">Take a look! <%= link_to 'Marin Cricket Club', 'https://www.marincricketclub.com/', target: 'blank' %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
